                    </mxGeometry>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="223" value="CreatedAt" style="shape=partialRectangle;connectable=0;fillColor=none;top=0;left=0;bottom=0;right=0;align=left;spacingLeft=6;overflow=hidden;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;rounded=1;fontSize=24;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;sketch=1;curveFitting=1;jiggle=2;" parent="221" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="72.75" width="385.25" height="42" as="geometry">
                        <mxRectangle width="385.25" height="42" as="alternateBounds"/>
                    </mxGeometry>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="226" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;As a Partner&lt;br/&gt;I want to sign up when I sign up I wait the platform&lt;br/&gt;to send me a payament gate so I can pay the fee&lt;br/&gt;but if the info i provide were wrong &lt;br/&gt;i want them to send me an email contians 3 componenets&lt;br/&gt;1st what is wrong and why&lt;br/&gt;2nd the OTP code for security &lt;br/&gt;3rd a url lead to the edit page where i edit the mess info and correct them&lt;br/&gt;if somehow i entered that url and miss out the OTP code&lt;br/&gt;and i only have 3 chances if i missed them all a new OTP code generate&lt;br/&gt;and resend to me and so on for 3 times then the the device is requesting &lt;br/&gt;is blocked unless the i chat with cutomer support and gave them reasons why&lt;br/&gt;i missed all that times. after i finish everything&lt;br/&gt;i want to log in, when i try to log in for i recive a OTP code and if&lt;br/&gt;i missed 3 time a new one generated and if i missed it all again for 3 times&lt;br/&gt;the device trying to log in is blocked unless chat with cutomer support &lt;br/&gt;and give them reasons why i missed all that times. so after i am logged in i&lt;br/&gt; can updated some info, but some infos required me to wait till &lt;br/&gt;the customer support check every updates and accept them&lt;br/&gt;and whether i update a sensitive data or not i get a notification with&lt;br/&gt;OTP code if i got it wrong for 3 time i recive a new OTP code for also&lt;br/&gt;3 times and if all wrong device requesting is blocked &lt;br/&gt;after i set it right it takes my request to waiting board if sensitive&lt;br/&gt;or just update if nomral data&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;i can also create, read, update, delete and search my own vehicles&lt;br/&gt;when i delete i get are you sure popup&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;i can report clients and rate them as well or even block them from seeing my&lt;br/&gt;vehicles again and when i rate them other partners can see the rating of that&lt;br/&gt;clients and only partners not clients cuz clients would get nothing if they&lt;br/&gt;know that this one is good or not, not like partners where they should know&lt;br/&gt;so they can cancle the clients booking or even block the clients who are&lt;br/&gt;less than 3 stars which each client is 5 stars max and 0 min &lt;br/&gt;or report the clients and if valid resons the client get blocked from the&lt;br/&gt;platform and can not get back unless he came someone else info&lt;br/&gt;cuz there are info can not be changed the if he even lied when he rent and &lt;br/&gt;go the the place where to get the vehcile he can not take it cuz the info &lt;br/&gt;in the website are no the same in his id card and just block the client&lt;br/&gt;with out anything but the only impact that is the client cannot see my &lt;br/&gt;product again&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;if someone rent one of our vehicles&lt;br/&gt;we can make it accept every booking automatic or manulay or hybird &lt;br/&gt;like if the user face the min requirements that means it accept automatic&lt;br/&gt;but if less than it get to pending or get rejected once the request applied&lt;br/&gt;these settings are in the profile where they can set&lt;br/&gt;min to accept and min to reject and if the client does not meet the min&lt;br/&gt;to reject or min to accept then the  user get to the pending stage&lt;br/&gt;and once every thing is good and the booking is accepted a notificatin comes&lt;br/&gt;to the partner or they can cancle those typeof notificatins and set a url&lt;br/&gt;and they can integrate with us by setting a url we send a post request to&lt;br/&gt;it and that url should accept certine type of data we proivd ein the doces&lt;br/&gt;if they want so if the url is not provided then a notification goes to the parter&lt;br/&gt;email or if they cancled the emails they should accept and check dayliy&lt;br/&gt;as well as the emails i should manage them like news are either enable or disable&lt;br/&gt;and when book event either enable or disable or i can set both email and the url&lt;br/&gt;integration&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;fontColor=default;fontStyle=0;fontSize=18;spacing=2;horizontal=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="-17" y="759" width="668" height="1264" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="227" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;As a Client&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;i want to sign in and when i sign in and produce data it should be valid and if not&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;nothing would happend but when i rent and go if anything was not right the&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;rent is gone but if i got somethign wrong and i&amp;nbsp; knew later i can edit it and just&lt;br&gt;for security i recie a OTP code and if wrong the same process happend i got 3 chanes&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;and 3 tiems for new generated OTP after that the device submiting is blocked&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;and can never send anything to the servce unless chat with customer support&lt;br&gt;and shows them reasonalbe resons&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;fontColor=default;fontStyle=0;fontSize=18;spacing=2;horizontal=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
